---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: "Sectors"
description: "Sectors Brunaþéttingar serves across Iceland — energy and utilities, aluminium, fishing, hospitals, schools, commercial, hotels, pharma."
permalink: /en/geirar/
bodyClass: sectors-page
eleventyNavigation:
  key: sectors-en
  order: 3
  parent: false
kicker: "Brunaþéttingar works across every major Icelandic industry."
intro:
  label: "Industry in Iceland"
  heading: "From the Hellisheiði power plant to the capital region's hospitals."
  paragraphs:
    - "We design, install and document technical insulation and fire sealing for the projects that keep the country running."
    - "Each sector has its own demands — temperature, hygiene, documentation — and we tune the system to each."
valueBand:
  label: "Each sector has its requirements"
  heading: "One company — eight sectors — <span class=\"value-band__highlight\">seven service lines</span>."
  paragraphs:
    - "Our work scales from a single building penetration to a full plant shutdown — same standards, same documentation, same crew."
cta:
  heading: "Ready to start your project? <span class=\"cta-band__highlight\">Get in touch.</span>"
  primaryHref: "/en/verdreiknir/"
  primaryLabel: "Get a quote"
  secondaryHref: "tel:+3548504405"
  secondaryLabel: "(+354) 850-4405"
---
{%- set sectors = collections['sectors-' + lang] | sort(false, false, 'data.order') %}
<section class="page-hero">
  <img class="page-hero__image" src="/img/iceland_alcoa_reydar.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="900">
  <div class="page-hero__scrim"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="page-hero__kicker">{{ kicker | safe }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sectors-page__content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sectors-intro">
      <div>
        <div class="sectors-intro__label">{{ intro.label }}</div>
        <h2>{{ intro.heading | safe }}</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        {%- for p in intro.paragraphs %}
        <p>{{ p | safe }}</p>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sector-grid">
      {%- for s in sectors %}
      <a class="sector-card" href="{{ s.url }}">
        <div class="sector-card__media">
          <img class="sector-card__media-img" src="{{ s.data.image }}" alt="" width="1200" height="900">
          <span class="sector-card__badge">{{ s.data.number }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sector-card__body">
          <h3>{{ s.data.title | safe }}</h3>
          <p>{{ s.data.description | safe }}</p>
          <ul class="sector-card__tags">
            {%- for t in s.data.tagLabels %}
            <li class="sector-card__tag">{{ t }}</li>
            {%- endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="value-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div>
        <div class="label">{{ valueBand.label }}</div>
        <h2>{{ valueBand.heading | safe }}</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        {%- for p in valueBand.paragraphs %}
        <p>{{ p | safe }}</p>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <h2>{{ cta.heading | safe }}</h2>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn primary" href="{{ cta.primaryHref }}"><span>{{ cta.primaryLabel }}</span> <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="{{ cta.secondaryHref }}"><span>{{ cta.secondaryLabel }}</span> <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
